1
00:00:27,300 --> 00:00:29,340
[Bride's Revenge]

2
00:00:29,740 --> 00:00:31,780
[Episode 14]

3
00:00:32,020 --> 00:00:34,780
[A Gentle Knife Cuts Deeper Than Any Other]

4
00:00:41,900 --> 00:00:44,340
(How dare he use
such despicable means to test me!)

5
00:00:45,140 --> 00:00:47,100
(What a monster!)

6
00:00:47,860 --> 00:00:50,340
(I'll make sure you die a gruesome death!)

7
00:00:52,220 --> 00:00:53,620
[Mu's Residence]

8
00:00:53,620 --> 00:00:54,860
Where did you get all that money

9
00:00:55,220 --> 00:00:56,900
to start your timber business?

10
00:00:59,420 --> 00:01:01,700
I have my own ways.

11
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:04,740
Did you earn the money yourself?

12
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:06,620
Our family

13
00:01:06,860 --> 00:01:08,380
runs a proper business.

14
00:01:08,900 --> 00:01:10,620
The world has already changed.

15
00:01:11,460 --> 00:01:12,500
You're up in your years.

16
00:01:13,700 --> 00:01:15,020
You should retire and return to the countryside

17
00:01:15,620 --> 00:01:17,220
to live the rest of your life in peace.

18
00:01:18,060 --> 00:01:18,820
Silence!

19
00:01:18,980 --> 00:01:20,900
How did I raise such an ungrateful child like you?

20
00:01:23,620 --> 00:01:25,100
Me? Ungrateful?

21
00:01:26,100 --> 00:01:27,540
All of you

22
00:01:27,700 --> 00:01:29,500
have always preferred my younger brother over me!

23
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:31,460
No matter what I do,

24
00:01:31,460 --> 00:01:32,660
I'll always be ignored.

25
00:01:33,020 --> 00:01:35,540
To you, I'll always be inferior to him!

26
00:01:35,940 --> 00:01:37,300
Blame yourself for not being

27
00:01:37,660 --> 00:01:38,820
as good as your brother!

28
00:01:39,700 --> 00:01:40,940
If your brother were still alive,

29
00:01:41,140 --> 00:01:43,820
he would never do this to his mother!

30
00:01:43,820 --> 00:01:45,180
That's all because

31
00:01:45,180 --> 00:01:46,700
I'm not your biological son!

32
00:01:57,140 --> 00:01:57,740
You…

33
00:01:58,580 --> 00:01:59,860
You know?

34
00:02:05,020 --> 00:02:07,260
When I learned of my origins,

35
00:02:08,060 --> 00:02:09,500
I finally understood

36
00:02:09,740 --> 00:02:11,020
why I was never able

37
00:02:11,020 --> 00:02:12,460
to get the same attention all these years.

38
00:02:13,460 --> 00:02:14,340
What gives?

39
00:02:15,140 --> 00:02:16,740
This family is what it is today

40
00:02:16,900 --> 00:02:19,340
because of the foundation my father built!

41
00:02:20,300 --> 00:02:22,580
Yet the Mu Family treats me like I'm a charity case.

42
00:02:24,220 --> 00:02:25,860
If my father were still alive,

43
00:02:26,420 --> 00:02:28,420
he would never let me fend for myself

44
00:02:28,460 --> 00:02:29,700
for all these years!

45
00:02:33,500 --> 00:02:34,700
You can't say that!

46
00:02:36,340 --> 00:02:37,700
All these years,

47
00:02:38,900 --> 00:02:39,620
we've raised you

48
00:02:39,620 --> 00:02:41,620
like our own son!

49
00:02:42,020 --> 00:02:43,300
We never mistreated you!

50
00:02:43,340 --> 00:02:45,420
That's only because the Mu Family owes me!

51
00:02:48,660 --> 00:02:50,140
But it's fine now.

52
00:02:50,380 --> 00:02:53,100
No one can tell me what to do anymore.

53
00:02:55,780 --> 00:02:59,060
I will have what I want.

54
00:03:13,700 --> 00:03:15,260
(Ever since I married him,)

55
00:03:15,620 --> 00:03:17,020
(Mu Ancheng sealed)

56
00:03:17,020 --> 00:03:19,340
(Anhe's room,)

57
00:03:19,340 --> 00:03:22,420
(claiming it would remind Madam of sad memories.)

58
00:03:22,420 --> 00:03:24,820
(Something important must be hidden here.)

59
00:04:18,100 --> 00:04:18,740
(This is the suitcase)

60
00:04:18,740 --> 00:04:20,380
(that contained the ransom for Anhe.)

61
00:04:28,820 --> 00:04:31,550
[50 taels]

62
00:04:31,900 --> 00:04:33,060
(No wonder)

63
00:04:33,060 --> 00:04:34,660
(Mu Ancheng was able
to fork out such a large sum of money)

64
00:04:34,660 --> 00:04:35,780
(to pay for my dowry.)

65
00:04:35,900 --> 00:04:37,300
(This was the money
that was supposed to save Anhe's life.)

66
00:04:37,740 --> 00:04:38,460
(I'm going to report this to the authority!)

67
00:04:38,860 --> 00:04:41,100
(You'll be put into jail, Mu Ancheng!)

68
00:04:43,420 --> 00:04:43,820
(No.)

69
00:04:44,460 --> 00:04:45,940
(I was the one who had the ransom)

70
00:04:46,180 --> 00:04:47,620
(but was unable to save Anhe.)

71
00:04:48,300 --> 00:04:50,580
(If I use this to accuse Mu Ancheng,)

72
00:04:50,820 --> 00:04:53,100
(it'll backfire on me
just like what happened before.)

73
00:04:54,380 --> 00:04:56,180
(I need the madam to find out)

74
00:04:56,180 --> 00:04:58,300
(that this money
is in Mu Ancheng's hands all along.)

75
00:05:14,580 --> 00:05:16,260
Take all of these away.

76
00:05:16,580 --> 00:05:17,140
Yes.

77
00:05:19,900 --> 00:05:21,260
What is the meaning of this?

78
00:05:24,020 --> 00:05:24,380
Mother.

79
00:05:24,540 --> 00:05:25,220
Ancheng said

80
00:05:25,500 --> 00:05:27,100
that you shouldn't bring these valuables with you

81
00:05:27,140 --> 00:05:28,500
back to the countryside

82
00:05:28,580 --> 00:05:29,860
and told me to take care of them for you.

83
00:05:32,500 --> 00:05:33,900
How dare you!

84
00:05:36,140 --> 00:05:37,260
These banknotes

85
00:05:37,900 --> 00:05:39,180
belong to the Ye Family.

86
00:05:39,980 --> 00:05:40,940
I'll be taking them.

87
00:05:43,060 --> 00:05:43,660
Don't you even think about it!

88
00:05:45,260 --> 00:05:46,380
I know

89
00:05:46,540 --> 00:05:48,140
Ancheng gave you these as your dowry

90
00:05:48,140 --> 00:05:49,220
out of his own pocket!

91
00:05:49,780 --> 00:05:50,740
They have nothing to do with you!

92
00:05:56,820 --> 00:05:57,540
These notes

93
00:05:58,140 --> 00:06:00,020
have my family's exclusive stamp on them.

94
00:06:00,900 --> 00:06:02,980
Just like the ransom for Anhe.

95
00:06:04,380 --> 00:06:05,380
If you refuse to accept this,

96
00:06:06,020 --> 00:06:06,980
then there's nothing I can do.

97
00:06:08,220 --> 00:06:10,020
Consider them a tribute from me
for your retirement.

98
00:06:13,580 --> 00:06:14,820
(I was wondering)

99
00:06:15,260 --> 00:06:17,460
(where Ancheng got all that money.)

100
00:06:18,180 --> 00:06:21,260
(Could this really be the ransom for Anhe?)

101
00:06:21,900 --> 00:06:22,940
Put those things down.

102
00:06:23,300 --> 00:06:23,740
Let's go.

103
00:06:24,260 --> 00:06:24,620
Yes.

104
00:06:24,740 --> 00:06:25,100
Yes.

105
00:06:35,460 --> 00:06:36,020
Madam,

106
00:06:37,140 --> 00:06:38,500
First Young Master sent word

107
00:06:38,500 --> 00:06:39,740
that the carriage is ready

108
00:06:39,740 --> 00:06:41,020
and asked when you will depart.

109
00:06:44,140 --> 00:06:44,980
I'm staying.

110
00:06:45,300 --> 00:06:46,740
I'm not going anywhere!

111
00:06:46,900 --> 00:06:47,460
Madam…

112
00:06:48,460 --> 00:06:50,860
He wants to leave me to rot in the countryside?

113
00:06:51,140 --> 00:06:52,180
I won't let him have his way!

114
00:06:52,180 --> 00:06:53,300
All right, all right. We won't leave.

115
00:06:53,300 --> 00:06:53,780
We'll stay.

116
00:06:55,300 --> 00:06:58,700
[Mu's Residence]

117
00:07:00,180 --> 00:07:01,260
This is a joint letter

118
00:07:01,540 --> 00:07:03,300
from all of the Mu Family's shopkeepers.

119
00:07:03,940 --> 00:07:05,740
They think that you're underqualified

120
00:07:06,140 --> 00:07:07,220
and not ready

121
00:07:07,220 --> 00:07:08,740
to take over the Mu Family's business yet.

122
00:07:09,260 --> 00:07:10,620
So they've signed this joint letter

123
00:07:10,900 --> 00:07:11,860
asking me to take the helm for you.

124
00:07:13,660 --> 00:07:14,220
Mother,

125
00:07:14,620 --> 00:07:16,020
didn't we agree

126
00:07:16,020 --> 00:07:16,940
that you would go back to the countryside

127
00:07:17,140 --> 00:07:18,060
and I would take charge

128
00:07:18,060 --> 00:07:19,620
of everything in the Mu Family?

129
00:07:22,420 --> 00:07:24,140
With so many shopkeepers showing concern,

130
00:07:24,420 --> 00:07:25,740
I can't possibly leave.

131
00:07:26,020 --> 00:07:28,420
So you're going to interfere until the end?

132
00:07:29,780 --> 00:07:30,740
I'm just

133
00:07:30,820 --> 00:07:32,540
safeguarding the business for you temporarily.

134
00:07:33,100 --> 00:07:33,900
Someday,

135
00:07:34,140 --> 00:07:35,660
all of this will be yours.

136
00:07:35,780 --> 00:07:36,900
No need to be impatient.

137
00:07:46,580 --> 00:07:47,900
The things in my room…

138
00:07:49,780 --> 00:07:51,340
I'll send them to your room right away.

139
00:07:51,420 --> 00:07:53,020
We can rest assured with you in charge,

140
00:07:53,100 --> 00:07:54,260
Mother.

141
00:07:55,820 --> 00:07:57,140
At least you know that.

142
00:07:58,900 --> 00:08:00,020
(Anhe,)

143
00:08:00,660 --> 00:08:04,180
(I will use your mother to avenge you.)

144
00:08:15,300 --> 00:08:17,460
♪The tangle of love and hate between us♪

145
00:08:17,700 --> 00:08:21,060
♪Caused me to regret it♪

146
00:08:22,420 --> 00:08:27,260
♪I'm afraid we can't change our fate in this life♪

147
00:08:28,580 --> 00:08:31,420
♪I do not fear. I do not hide♪

148
00:08:32,020 --> 00:08:34,900
♪I can no longer bear the pain♪

149
00:08:35,460 --> 00:08:42,100
♪It grows as time passes♪

150
00:08:42,700 --> 00:08:44,340
♪Time will not tell you♪

151
00:08:44,780 --> 00:08:46,380
♪That I have been missing you♪

152
00:08:46,700 --> 00:08:49,140
♪You are all I think about♪

153
00:08:49,780 --> 00:08:51,100
♪No matter♪

154
00:08:51,260 --> 00:08:52,540
♪How harshly♪

155
00:08:52,540 --> 00:08:56,220
♪Life treats me♪

156
00:08:56,860 --> 00:08:58,260
♪I can only let go of my hate♪

157
00:08:58,460 --> 00:08:59,980
♪Not my love♪

158
00:09:00,460 --> 00:09:03,860
♪We promised each other life-long love♪

159
00:09:04,140 --> 00:09:10,340
♪Hopefully, we will keep that promise♪
